body: Let's see: Yatuzaki/Yatsuzaki's part 9/10, Tekorun's part 8/10, Palco Nagashima's part 7/10, the one with the cat maid 6/10 Hayashida Toranosuke's part 6/10 and Nekokokazuma 6/10, this anthology is has pretty much quite a decent amount of quality with minor faults with the art work and sex scenes, and some parts not having much thrill or impact, it needed a bit more intensity.
